        <div className="bg-gray-950/40 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <div className="grid grid-cols-[1fr_150px_100px_140px_120px] gap-4 px-8 py-4 border-b border-white/5 text-[10px] font-black text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] bg-gray-900/20">
            <span>Identificaci├â┬│n y Descripci├â┬│n</span>
            <span className="text-center">Categor├â┬¡a</span>
            <span className="text-center">Unidad</span>
            <span className="text-right">Precio Base</span>
            <span className="text-right pr-4">Acciones</span>
          </div>

          <div className="divide-y divide-white/5">
